data.description: Looking for a beautifully updated home in Rosamond? This gem has 3 bedrooms, 2 full baths plus a den or additional bedroom and comes with a GREAT PRICE! It features newer flooring, Samsung Stainless Steel appliances, plantation shutters in every bedroom and kitchen. Nice spacious kitchen with lots of cabinetry. Ample living room with a cozy fireplace for these chilly winter nights. A separate dining area. Nice size master bedroom with ensuite bathroom: his and her sinks, walk-in closet and slider leading to the back. The AC/Heater unit along with all ducting and insulation is moderately new. Plus, two attic fans were also installed for even more proficiency. Newer energy efficient windows were installed about 10 years ago. New all black light fixture and rocker switches. Nice backyard with lattice patio and a dog run on the side. Close to 14 FWY and Edwards AFB. A must see! You can qualify to purchase this home with ZERO down, USDA financing. Call for more information!
